{
  "stem": "9665.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't have a name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They made stockings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got together in 1959-- '58, '59.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got together, and it was a very pleasant relationship, until-- now I have to be very careful-- 1962.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we wanted to be public, so I went-- I bought, what we call, the back door entrance toward Roslyn Hosiery-- national hosiery mills.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were the public company.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a public company, you can't sell anything for cash.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I want to leave it as such, because it doesn't make sense to go any further.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because then, I went to the Liebermans, and I said, we can't be together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I paid them out, in 1963, 380,000 pounds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Liebermans bought, with 380,000 pounds, for 20 million pounds real estate, because it was the lowest ever in Australia-- '63, '64.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, it was a chance which I had, because both of them were in a gamble, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What could they lose?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because at the time, it was possible to buy something for 10% deposit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had 15% deposit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went into-- I got-- I-- I-- they-- we were leaving each other's company in 1963.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was together with Jan Laos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by that time, we were in-- you know, how did we get the machines?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I forget to tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a Bonds Hosiery Mill in Rosebery, where we can only import machines for replacement, because we had these giants-- Prestige, Holeproof-- making stockings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had Beaumont.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had Nightingale, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't exist anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After Kolotex got big, we wiped them off them market.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that is, we bought an old machine, old hosiery machine, once in Rosebery.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
